            <h3 id="contributing">Contributing</h3>
                            
            <p>The Alambic project is developed on BitBucket: <a href="https://bitbucket.org/BorisBaldassari/alambic">https://bitbucket.org/BorisBaldassari/alambic</a>.<p> 

            <p>It is public and open to contributions. One can clone the repository from there, or contribute to the project in many ways:</p>

              <ul>
