                <li>The wiki, for the developer and user documentation: <a href="https://bitbucket.org/BorisBaldassari/alambic/wiki/">https://bitbucket.org/BorisBaldassari/alambic/wiki/</a>. You should be able to edit the pages and add your experience and knowledge.</li>
